<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mḥtạjlk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹nt wḥdk ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lk tsnd ḍʿfy tqwyny
 ạ̹nt trsy wṣkẖry wḥṣny wm ạlḥfrh tnjyny)2
 1-ạ̹nt wḥdk ḥạrb ʿny wf ḥḍn qlbk tdạryny
 mhmạ ạ̉ḥạwl wḥdy yạrby ạlkẖṭyh btgẖryny
 bạṭlb sẖkẖṣk tyjy bwʿdk (trfʿny kmạn tḥmyny)2
 2- qạṣd bạbk tkẖlʿ ʿny sẖry bdmk gẖṭyny
 ạ̹sẖfy nfsy wdẖly wḥyrty w ạ̹nt brwḥk ạ̹ḥyyny
 ạ̉nẓr rby lạ̉rḍy ạlʿṭsẖy̱( ạ̹rwyhạ kmạn ạ̹rwyny)2
 3-ạ̉nt wḥdk ạ̉nạ mntẓrk tḥfẓny wtʿdyny
 fyk ạlqwh wlyk ạlqdrh tkfyny wtgẖnyny
 ạ̹nt bs btsẖbʿ qlby( yạlly bạlgẖạly sẖạryny)2</lyrics>
